 job at the carnival.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 8\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 8\n| Title               = The Thing Blanks Out\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|9|29}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 9\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 9\n| Title               = The Thing Meets the Clunk\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|6}}\n| ShortSummary        = Dr. Quimby's new robot goes rogue and causes trouble for The Thing.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 10\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 10\n| Title               = Beach Party Crashers\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|6}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 11\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 11\n| Title               = Decepto the Great\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|13}}\n| ShortSummary        = A magician, Decepto the Great, comes to town, planning on stealing from the school kids.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 12\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 12\n| Title               = The Thing's the Play\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|13}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 13\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 13\n| Title               = Double Trouble for the Thing\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|20}}\n| ShortSummary        = An evil scientist creates a robot Thing to rob the citizens and make them think The Thing has gone bad.\n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 14\n| EpisodeNumber2      = 14\n| Title               = To Thing or Not to Thing\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|1979|10|20}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n| LineColor           = #FF681F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 15\n| Episo